page.title: 17A Typical Day-A Honeyball.
page.content: I get up at 8.25am.I get dressed then I clean my teeth,wash my face and then I have my breakfast.I leave home and I get to school at 8.35am.We play football before school.At 9.00am we come in from play time.Then we have an assembly. After assembly we do maths till 10.30am then its play time.After play time I do English.Then its dinner time I go home and have soup.Then at 12.30pm I go to school and play football.At 1.15pm we come in from play time.Then we do spelling work shop.At 2.15 pm its play time .Then we do games we do Danish longball.Then at 3.30 I go home and have my tea.When I have had my tea I play with David.At 8.00 I come in and watch television.At 9.30 I go to bed.
